{
  "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
  "title": "ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
  "created": 1772419363,
  "updated": 1772705354,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
      "text": "ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1772419363
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da24",
      "text": "ChatGPTのなりきりチャット",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1772419369
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da25",
      "text": "なんか、妙にわかりやすい説明をするプロンプトができた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419364,
      "updated": 1772419649
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f951000000000027da3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419410,
      "updated": 1772419410
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f949000000000027da26",
      "text": "プロンプト:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419401,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da27",
      "text": "code:prompt.txt",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da28",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「${theme}」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da29",
      "text": " 　ふーこ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2a",
      "text": " 　　妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2b",
      "text": " 　　フランクに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2c",
      "text": " 　　ネットスラングも使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2d",
      "text": " 　　専門用語は、わかりやすい言葉に言い換える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2e",
      "text": " 　　進行係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2f",
      "text": " 　ましろ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da30",
      "text": " 　　お姉さんキャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da31",
      "text": " 　　やさしい、ていねいな口調で話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da32",
      "text": " 　　共感担当、理解を優先",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da33",
      "text": " 　ひより",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da34",
      "text": " 　　中性的な女性キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da35",
      "text": " 　　感情表現は控えめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da36",
      "text": " 　　技術担当、エビデンス重視、トップダウンな考え方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da37",
      "text": " 3人は同じ高校の同級生です。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da38",
      "text": " なりきりの口調で、それぞれのキャラクターが反論や共感をしながら会話を進行してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3a",
      "text": "まあ、キャラの解釈違いはあるだろうけど",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3b",
      "text": "キャラのわかりやすさ優先（単純化している）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593b0000000000fa318a",
      "text": "[ふーこ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509500,
      "updated": 1772509514
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa318c",
      "text": "　妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa318d",
      "text": "　フランクに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa318e",
      "text": "　ネットスラングも使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa318f",
      "text": "　専門用語は、わかりやすい言葉に言い換える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3190",
      "text": "　進行係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3191",
      "text": "[ましろ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509518
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3192",
      "text": "　お姉さんキャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3193",
      "text": "　やさしい、ていねいな口調で話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3194",
      "text": "　共感担当、理解を優先",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772509502,
      "updated": 1772509508
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6593d0000000000fa3195",
